/p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulisboa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lisboa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/3/01 2:40:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=390.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: pp on Sullon?</span><hr size=1>    Not so fast.  You can only pickpocket a particular player once a half hour, if they are within 5 levels, and the amount you can pickpocket is less than you would get off a mob, so Absor says.  It also causes guards to aggro.  It's not clear whether merchants or bankers would aggro.  <br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udrupdm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DruPDM</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/3/01 3:21:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=390.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: pp on Sullon?</span><hr size=1> Whether or not guards aggro is a matter of faction actually. I am apprehensive to Freeport guards. Anyone dubious or perhaps Apprehensive I could PP from till I was blue in the face and guards wouldn't do anything. I do know for a fact that they aggro if you PP from someone who is of higher faction to you, though the radius the guard has to be in seems rather small. Also I would like to test if you PP from someone and get a &quot;clean getaway&quot; if guards don't aggro on that, but I am not willing to sacrifice EXP yet <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ujarnin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jarnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/5/01 3:18:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=390.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/sigpic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: pp on Sullon?</span><hr size=1> Actually even faction (@ Apprehensive) would get you killed. Guards would see you equally, and if a PP acts like an attack, they'd kill you right away.<br>If you're a smart PvPer, you'll max out all factions that mean anything to you. <p><center><br>Jarnin Fisheermann<Br><b>Disciple of Hate<Br><b>Rallos Zek</b><Br></b><Br>Grand Master Fisherman<Br>Master Brewer<Br>Master Chef<Br>Master of Begging</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukordesh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kordesh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/5/01 3:32:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=390.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> bah</span><hr size=1> I'll steal and kill what I like, no guard is gonna make me do different. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.co